  "original_title": "5 \u0bae\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0ba8\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc8 \u0bae\u0bc0\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b95 \u0bae\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd - \u0bae\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf \u0bb5\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf \u0b86\u0bb3\u0bc1\u0ba8\u0bb0\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Country can be recovered within 5 months - Central Bank Governor",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Governor of the Central Bank of Sri Lanka Nandalal Weerasinghe Weerasinghe said that the country can be recovered from the economic crisis within 5 months.",
        "The Governor of the Central Bank of Sri Lanka has given an explanation to an international media about how the country will recover from the economic crisis.",
        "The Governor of the Central Bank of Sri Lanka Kalanithi Nandalal Weerasinghe said that there is a clear program to rescue the country from the economic crisis.",
        "He further said that Sri Lanka can recover from the current economic crisis within 5 months if this program is followed."
      ],
